Chegg,Affiliate,API,is,a,book,rental,portal,that,allows,users,to,search,textbook,titles,and,pricing,details,The,provider,of,the,API,Chegg,mainly,rents,out,textbooks,and,distributes,etextbooks,at,subsidized,rates,through,its,online,library,portal,The,API,is,ideal,for,Chegg,affiliated,developers,that,run,shopping,sites,that,compare,rental,prices,of,textbooks,and,other,stationery,items,Access,to,the,API,s,documentation,must,be,requested,through,email,and,is,restricted,to,developers,with,approved,Chegg,affiliate,accounts